            "name": "Description",
            "type": "section",
            "html": "An infernal paradox at once wondrous and terrifying, tempting and blasphemous, Basileus serves as the herald of Asmodeus and the harbinger of Hell\u2019s will. Few who have met him survive the experience unchanged, for he is the very word of Hell."
